@DATABASE "Easy"
@WIDTH 77
@NODE "intro" "Introduction"
@PREV "MAIN"
@TOC "MAIN"
Introduction

With Easylink 1.0 it is possible to connect an Amiga and a PC Computer via
a @{"nullmodem-cable" LINK "cable"} and to exchange data between them. 
As Easylink works with a PAR-protocoll it is possible to use Easylink in
multitasking environement.

@ENDNODE

